For the idea and creation of Lab Room B

To play this map properly you have to trigger the escape by shooting/activating the objects at the last 2 screenshots.

**Extra Info:**
- 66 spawnpoints (33 each team)
- Recruires No-Block to be enabled
- Complete time minimum are 7 minutes and 0 seconds.
- Complete time maximum are 9 minutes.
- Map contains a drivable crane

**Known bugs/improvements:**
None yet.

**Update information**
- V1_1
Fixed bugs: Elevator waiting time fixed; Falling of plane fixed.
Changes: Speed of planes increased (from 200 to 512); Added a second door in spawn; Improved zombie block first sattelite; Added a 6th song to the radio
